Document: AnimatedTexture
Path: godot/classes/class_animatedtexture.rst
Summary: Class reference for AnimatedTexture, covering its identity, description, and inheritance chain.

AnimatedTexture is a class that extends Texture and provides functionality for animating textures over time. It inherits from Texture and adds properties and methods to control animation frames, speed, and playback behavior. The class is used to create animated textures in Godot projects, allowing for effects like blinking lights, rotating icons, or frame-based animations. Key Rule: AnimatedTexture requires at least one frame to function properly.
